title: King Solomon's Reef Cafe and Lounge
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A local hang-out with a jukebox, Ms Pac-Man, Galaga and Frogger arcade games. Breakfast is served all day. Veg include buffalo tempeh sandwich with house-made vegan ranch, house-made veggie burgers (vegetarian), tempeh hash (vegan), chicken fried tofu burger (vegan), sesame tofu sandwich (vegan), chicken fried tofu strips (vegan) and has vegan pie.
